OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778861473
OL,3,CSouthampton ask EFL for time to
OL,4,Cconduct internal review into 'spygate'
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FSouthampton have asked to be given
OL,8,Ftime to conduct an internal review
OL,9,Finto the circumstances surrounding the
OL,10,F'spygate' scandal ahead of their
OL,11,Fcrucial Championship play-off second-
OL,12,Fleg tie against Middlesbrough on
OL,13,FTuesday night (12 May).
OL,15,FIt is alleged a member of Southampton
OL,16,Fstaff was caught trying to observe a
OL,17,FMiddlesbrough training session last
OL,18,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
