FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778861473
OL,3,CSouthampton ask EFL for time to
OL,4,Cconduct internal review into 'spygate'
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe club were charged on Friday by the
OL,8,FEFL, who asked an independent
OL,9,Fdisciplinary commission to shorten the
OL,10,Fresponse period from the usual 14 days
OL,11,Fand to list a hearing "at the earliest
OL,12,Fopportunity".
OL,14,FHowever, Southampton insist it is
OL,15,Fvital they be given adequate time to
OL,16,Freview the matter and respond to the
OL,17,Fcharge properly. The Championship play-
OL,18,Foff final is scheduled for May 23.
OL,26,@sD@WOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778861473
OL,3,CSouthampton ask EFL for time to
OL,4,Cconduct internal review into 'spygate'
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FSouthampton chief executive Phil
OL,8,FParsons told the club's official
OL,9,Fwebsite: "The club is fully co-
OL,10,Foperating with the EFL and the
OL,11,Fdisciplinary commission, whilst also
OL,12,Fundertaking an internal review to
OL,13,Fensure that all facts and context are
OL,14,Fproperly understood.
OL,16,F"Given the intensity of the fixture
OL,17,Fschedule and the short turnaround
OL,18,Fbetween matches, we have requested
OL,19,Ftime to complete that process
OL,20,Fthoroughly and responsibly.
OL,26,@qD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
