FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778861473
OL,3,CSouthampton ask EFL for time to
OL,4,Cconduct internal review into 'spygate'
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"We understand the discussion and
OL,8,Fspeculation that has followed over
OL,9,Frecent days, but we also believe it is
OL,10,Fimportant that the full context is
OL,11,Festablished before conclusions are
OL,12,Fdrawn."
OL,14,FSaints head coach Tonda Eckert refused
OL,15,Fto answer questions about the
OL,16,Fallegations at the post-match press
OL,17,Fconference following the first leg `
OL,18,Fwhich ended goalless ` at
OL,19,FMiddlesbrough on Saturday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
