PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1778861473
OL,3,CSouthampton ask EFL for time to
OL,4,Cconduct internal review into 'spygate'
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FHis Boro counterpart, Kim Hellberg,
OL,8,Fsaid after the first match: "It's a
OL,9,Fweird situation. I couldn't believe my
OL,10,Feyes or ears when heard it, couldn't
OL,11,Fbelieve it when someone told me for
OL,12,Fthe second time or the third.
OL,14,F"But if someone makes decisions to go
OL,15,Fand try to cheat, that's clear and it
OL,16,Fwill be interesting to see what
OL,17,Fhappens with that."
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@AOUyD@SO]
